      <title>特朗普在空中相撞后抨击联邦航空管理局多元化计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-attacks-faa-diversity-programs-following-mid-air-collision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普几乎没有提供关于周三美国航空集团公司一架支线飞机与一架军用直升机在华盛顿发生致命空难的原因的新信息，而是将责任归咎于多元化、公平和包容计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-attacks-faa-diversity-programs-following-mid-air-collision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 17:25:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>默茨力争以新的移民强硬路线确保德国获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/german-conservative-hard-line-migration-shift-is-calculated-ploy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据了解弗里德里希·梅尔茨想法的人士称，他在移民问题上采取强硬路线是这位德国保守党领袖精心策划的策略，目的是平衡极右翼势力，并在摇摆不定的选民中取得突破。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/german-conservative-hard-line-migration-shift-is-calculated-ploy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 16:58:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果东部战争致数百万人面临传染病风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/war-in-congo-s-east-puts-millions-at-risk-of-infectious-disease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲首席卫生咨询机构称，卢旺达支持的叛军与刚果军队之间的战斗已使数百万人面临因疾病蔓延而死亡的高风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/war-in-congo-s-east-puts-millions-at-risk-of-infectious-disease</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 16:42:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>观察人士称莫桑比克选举存在“严重缺陷”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/mozambique-election-tainted-by-serious-flaws-observers-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟观察团在一份报告中指出，莫桑比克十月份备受争议的选举“充满异常和严重缺陷”，这进一步证实了反对党对选举结果的广泛谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/mozambique-election-tainted-by-serious-flaws-observers-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 16:38:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
