      <title>大规模抗议活动为何考验塞尔维亚长期统治者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/why-serbia-s-mass-protests-leave-president-vucic-more-vulnerable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚各地的大规模抗议活动暴露了总统亚历山大·武契奇十多年统治的裂痕。]]></description>
